    "spell": {
        "name": "Holy Cascade",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You call upon sacred energy to amplify a vial of holy water, tossing it an incredible distance. It explodes in an enormous burst that deals 3d6 bludgeoning damage to creatures in the area from the cascade of water. The water deals an additional 6d6 spirit damage to creatures with the unholy trait in the area.",
